					<li>Thousands of compliments and thank you messages earned by professionals over the course of their professional careers stay locked in their emails and messengers, waiting to be archived and never reaching their full potential
					</li>
					<li>Most reward system put in place by companies are totally closed applications, that do not let employees take away their earned compliments and reputation with them, when they switch jobs, which prevents them from building their proof of experience. It also prevents employers from reaching an easy and reliable means of verifying a candidateís experience.
					</li>
					<li>Need a means to ease off steam and break the ice, to pave way for a more positive work culture
					</li>
					<li>Employee satisfaction is a huge metric which is totally ignored in many workplaces. Most importance is paid at sales, customer satisfaction and retention etc, but never on the employeeís satisfaction that directly drives all aspects of business including sales and customer service etc
					</li>
					<li>Many times, employees who go out of their way to help others don't get much in return, or at least nothing strong enough to help them with their careers, reputation or provide a monetary value
